NEW YORK TIMES CO; ACQUISITIONS; DIVESTMENT; CABLE TELEVISION; MINORITY OWNED 
BUSINESS; COMCAST CORP; LENFEST COMMUNICATIONS INC; LLEWELLYN, J BRUCE 
</P>
