<P>
Because inaccurate information was supplied to The Times Orange County Edition, 
a story and table in Tuesday's Business section contained incorrect figures for 
average fourth-quarter office rents in Orange County as calculated by Grubb 
&amp; Ellis Co. The correct figures are: John Wayne Airport area, $1.25 to 
$2.60 per square foot per month; south county, $1.25 to $1.85; central county, 
$1.05 to $2.15; north county, $1 to $2; and west county, $1.25 to $2.25. 
